                     <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS JONES</hi> (18)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18610923-759-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18610923-759-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18610923-759-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
